title: BRIEF-Ecommerce Alliance prelim H1 EBITDA turns to profit of EUR 861,000
text:
BRIEF-Ecommerce Alliance prelim H1 EBITDA turns to profit of EUR 861,000 Sept 3 
Sept 3 Ecommerce Alliance AG : 
* H1 preliminary EBITDA 861,000 euros (last year loss 142,000 euros) 
* Preliminary H1 revenue of 40.174 million euros ($45 million)versus 44.246 million euros year ago Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.8862 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom) Trending On Reuters
